		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName> <date>20. April 1830</date>.</p>
				<p>My dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">So favorable an opportunity as this&#44; cannot escape<lb/> me to say a few words to you.  after the lapse of time intervened.<lb/>  The state of our <sic>uncle&#39;</sic> health is exceedingly delicate&#44; his limbs will<lb/> scarcely bear him along.  So debilitated is he by the wretched cough<lb/> <sic>attendent</sic> on the asthma.  rest has he now by day or night and altho<lb/> he has had strength enough to crawl to my office&#44; I really think he<lb/> will <add>not</add> get home without extreme fatigue.  I do not mention these facts<lb/> with a view of inducing you to come on should it interfere in your<lb/> <sic>arrangments</sic>&#44; but I am certain a few days of your company with Uncle<lb/> would so gratify him that the experiment is worth trying.  Could you<lb/> not be spared a few days next week&#63;  I am not so sure that I am<lb/> not taking a pain myself&#44; a reparability in <add>&#63;</add> remarks that might<lb/> induce you to come on at all hazards.  Our friend <persName>W. Etting</persName> will take<lb/> you to our debilitated &#38; <sic>feable</sic> uncle <add>&#63;</add> and I am only giving<lb/> you my own impression what I think would delight him.  Contrary to<lb/> any the leach<add>&#63;</add> idea that I had made this communication&#44; hence<lb/> <hi rend="underline">should</hi> you come say that your brain that much was sick and having</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>a few days leisure&#44; you came over to see him.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Mama has been confined to her bed &#38; room for some weeks.<lb/>  <add>&#63;</add> so far recoverd. I as to speak of coming down <add>Hebrew</add> God willing.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">A letter from <placeName><sic>Cincinnatti</sic></placeName> yesterday all well &#38; changes in state gov.<add>&#63;</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Happiness attend</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">you.</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><add>&#63;</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><hi rend="underline"><persName role="author">W. Judah</persName></hi></p>
			<pb n="2V"/>
				<p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leezer</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">attention</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><persName>Mr. <add>&#63;</add> Etting</persName>. <hi rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></hi></p>
